latestIgtvVideos.caption: Our bright and sunny travel days have a certain delight in them (helped a lot by the weather, for sure!) and a certain liberation: tossed over hair, a bag freely slung across the shoulder, the heaviest possible pair of Basanti earrings our earlobes could muster ( yes, that’s the silver in our armor!) and our carefully chosen attire to match the vibe- within and without.
